overview: Mr Frick has graduated from the University of Uppsala with a BSc degree in Business and Administration. He has over 25 years of international company experience at leading positions in the biotechnology sector, primarily at Pharmacia where he spent in total 14 years. He also has experience from a large number of exits and successful capital raising activities as well as over 10 years experience from working on boards in Sweden and internationally including experience as a chairman. He is currently serving on the Board of the Irish/US biotech company Elan.
